  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0dd6 \u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba\u0da7 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0ddd\u0d9c\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An order to give the money found in the presidential palace to the court",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Mr. Thilina Gamage today ordered Chief Inspector Sagara Liyanage of the Fort Police Station to hand over to the court immediately the amount of Rs.",
        "The Magistrate issued this order based on a notice given by the President's Counsel Mr. Rienzi Arsakularatne that more than three weeks have passed since the protesters handed over this amount of Rupees one crore seventy eight lakh fifty thousand to the police but no report or notification has been made by the Fort Police.",
        "These facts were presented when four activists who were arrested by the Fort Police were brought before the court stating that they had illegally entered the Araliyagaha Mandir and were members of an illegal crowd.",
        "Taking into account the facts presented, the court ordered that the amount be immediately handed over to the court and set bail for the four suspects.",
        "Accordingly, the court decided to release one of the suspects on bail of Rs 5 lakh each. Kusal Sadaruwan, Abdul Kader Abdul Khalil, Jeyaram Jayakumar and Jeyaram Jeyaraj were thus released on bail."
      ],
